---
const services = [
  {
    title: "Meeting Prep Briefs",
    description: "Automated dossiers before every scheduled call. Company background, recent news, relationship history—compiled automatically.",
    icon: "briefcase",
  },
  {
    title: "Relationship Coverage Alerts",
    description: "Know when key contacts haven't heard from you in 60/90/120 days. Stop letting relationships go cold.",
    icon: "users",
  },
  {
    title: "Outreach Ghostwriter",
    description: "Draft personalized emails based on triggers and contact context. Maintain your voice, eliminate the blank page problem.",
    icon: "pencil",
  },
];
---

<section id="whats-next" class="py-24 px-8 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6 text-navy">
        Once you see how this works...
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-stone font-medium">
        Most clients start with portfolio news monitoring, then add:
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-card grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      {services.map((service) => (
        <div class="bg-ivory p-8 border border-stone/30 border-dashed">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold/20 border border-gold/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            {service.icon === "briefcase" && (
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
            )}
            {service.icon === "users" && (
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
              </svg>
            )}
            {service.icon === "pencil" && (
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
              </svg>
            )}
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-3">{service.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal leading-relaxed">{service.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Closing paragraph -->
    <p class="text-lg text-charcoal leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
      These automations work together as a full revenue operations system—but you don't need to buy the bundle upfront. Start with what matters most, expand when you're ready.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
